  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8c8f527a39e446e5749ff38c164861bb.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8c8f527a39e446e5749ff38c164861bb.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8c8f527a39e446e5749ff38c164861bb.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/fa41593c00af72694c1f496a84b05c7d.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand against the undead hordes in a campaign inspired by fantasy classics. Discover the continent of Aganor across many challenging missions, push back the darkness, and protect your people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/f012c72265f75ab29f6c9962316d8dfc.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use the day to gather resources, fortify your town, and explore the surrounding lands. When the night falls, defend your people and their homes against the waves of enemies, until the break of dawn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8fbcdaf09a153d1960ea97feb6418a49.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8fbcdaf09a153d1960ea97feb6418a49.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8fbcdaf09a153d1960ea97feb6418a49.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/92884d56da103a1e1f19c080b3a38456.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the challenges with the help of legendary heroes - wizards, warriors, and more. Utilize their varied skills, level them up, and arm them with powerful artifacts won throughout your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/433a3905027c4070964cea9c2e774352.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/433a3905027c4070964cea9c2e774352.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/433a3905027c4070964cea9c2e774352.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/2f0dba61238dd361823b4ff98614190c.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own scenarios, maps, quests, and even whole, scripted campaigns with an extensive in-game editor. Share your creations with other players and set your imagination free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/9777a9981656ca7a663db2b40fa8a116.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test yourself in a challenging survival mode, where every night brings new, growing terrors. Survive the onslaught, and rebuild every morning to face the undead hordes again. Fight until you win glory… or reprieve in death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/6c697b80ec96f8b39fe2674c4baca614.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/6c697b80ec96f8b39fe2674c4baca614.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/6c697b80ec96f8b39fe2674c4baca614.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8c8f527a39e446e5749ff38c164861bb.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8c8f527a39e446e5749ff38c164861bb.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8c8f527a39e446e5749ff38c164861bb.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/fa41593c00af72694c1f496a84b05c7d.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand against the undead hordes in a campaign inspired by fantasy classics. Discover the continent of Aganor across many challenging missions, push back the darkness, and protect your people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/f012c72265f75ab29f6c9962316d8dfc.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use the day to gather resources, fortify your town, and explore the surrounding lands. When the night falls, defend your people and their homes against the waves of enemies, until the break of dawn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8fbcdaf09a153d1960ea97feb6418a49.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8fbcdaf09a153d1960ea97feb6418a49.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/8fbcdaf09a153d1960ea97feb6418a49.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/92884d56da103a1e1f19c080b3a38456.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the challenges with the help of legendary heroes - wizards, warriors, and more. Utilize their varied skills, level them up, and arm them with powerful artifacts won throughout your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/433a3905027c4070964cea9c2e774352.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/433a3905027c4070964cea9c2e774352.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/433a3905027c4070964cea9c2e774352.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/2f0dba61238dd361823b4ff98614190c.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own scenarios, maps, quests, and even whole, scripted campaigns with an extensive in-game editor. Share your creations with other players and set your imagination free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/9777a9981656ca7a663db2b40fa8a116.webp?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test yourself in a challenging survival mode, where every night brings new, growing terrors. Survive the onslaught, and rebuild every morning to face the undead hordes again. Fight until you win glory… or reprieve in death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/6c697b80ec96f8b39fe2674c4baca614.poster.avif?t=1763378013\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/6c697b80ec96f8b39fe2674c4baca614.webm?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/6c697b80ec96f8b39fe2674c4baca614.mp4?t=1763378013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
